    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bread 是一款有趣且简单的点击游戏，包含可收集物品。不断点击以获得更多面包屑，并且每 2 小时可获得一个随机 Bread。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>每 2 小时掉落（每日最多 12 个）*:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 65% Common</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 30% Uncommon</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 5% Rare</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 1 in 1 500 000 Epic</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 1 in 15 000 000 Legendary</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* 掉落率可能会有所变动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>特色内容：</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 物品掉落</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 可装备皮肤</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 社区市场</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 成就系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131610/extras/da506e786a766e98f6ac63383b6888d2.avif?t=1751964575\" width=384 height=384 /></span></p>",
